item.title: My first Chapter
item.description: I can only say that I have seen a lot of this kind of thing. I just want to say that I understand everything and I don’t want to say much if I don’t understand it. Fine details, don’t ask the reason. There are too many interests involved here. It’s not good for you and me. You don’t know. The rest of me can only say that the water is too deep and involves a lot of things.
